{"tid":924991,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"【劈價未停火】嘉湖山莊套三房 兩個月平190萬","createTime":"2018-12-02T13:39:50.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-03T02:37:50.000Z","uid":174649,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"d3229871528b1df34cfbc2526e9f62eebdc35ee9","tid":924991,"uid":174649,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-02T13:39:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20181202/large/1543744109_bfcd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20181202%2Flarge%2F1543744109_bfcd.jpg&h=896d51ea&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n雖然中美貿易戰氣氛緩和，但二手樓劈價尚未停火。天水圍嘉湖山莊近期交投回暖，本周末暫錄6宗成交，其中一宗屬大劈價，套三房僅售548萬元。<br />\n<br />\n消息指賞湖居6座極高層A室，實用面積636方呎，三房連主人套房間隔，屬大單邊優質戶，座向西北，望中央公園開揚景，上月中叫價仍企硬690萬元，屬鎖匙盤，剛大幅減價逾百萬至548萬元沽出，呎價8,616元。翠湖居3座高層A室，實用面積636方呎，景觀接近，同樣望中央公園，但座向東南，質素更高，今年10月以738萬元沽出，呎價11,604元，最新成交較之低190萬元或26%。"},{"pid":"b81fc6fb89cd354c046a0e0c212e95f3c84011c3","tid":924991,"uid":51933,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-02T13:41:56.000Z","msg":"上月中叫價仍企硬690萬元，屬鎖匙盤，剛大幅減價逾百萬至548萬元沽出<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n廢淡無出色<br />\n企硬呀應該 <br />\n下年個盤值1000萬"},{"pid":"a06a128bdb949e7f34ae71365e362c1f78554706","tid":924991,"uid":195998,"like":5,"dislike":2,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-02T13:46:15.000Z","msg":"呢d 西樓 百幾二百果時唔買<br />\n<br />\n700萬先黎買"},{"pid":"09e1b1857c0460c2841b3b10a19eee125369b825","tid":924991,"uid":57226,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-02T13:54:34.000Z","msg":"好唔好住先? 天水圍"},{"pid":"2a9cb3bdbaece9c0458294337479780c1ea4aea6","tid":924991,"uid":159313,